00:50:48,246 --> 00:50:50,914
See, in a couple of days,
this'll be gone.

680
00:50:50,915 --> 00:50:54,918
Sandblasted away or
covered by someone else's paint.

681
00:50:54,919 --> 00:50:56,804
That's okay, 'cause,

682
00:50:56,805 --> 00:50:59,890
I don't want anyone
getting too attached to it.

683
00:50:59,891 --> 00:51:02,894
So... wanna make out
with me now?

684
00:51:06,014 --> 00:51:08,766
Bet you thought I was serious.

685
00:51:29,838 --> 00:51:31,538
Whoa!

686
00:51:31,539 --> 00:51:32,790
What the hell was that?

687
00:51:32,791 --> 00:51:33,957
Weren't you lookin'?

688
00:51:33,958 --> 00:51:35,843
Could you next time
give me a little warning?

