the day you were doin' the 360 spins...

737
00:54:49,120 --> 00:54:50,203
Davies donuts.
You liked those, huh?

738
00:54:50,204 --> 00:54:51,204
Pretty cool?

739
00:54:51,205 --> 00:54:52,706
Davies donuts?

740
00:54:52,707 --> 00:54:55,909
Yeah, I copied them off
a guy named Vic Davies.

741
00:54:55,910 --> 00:54:58,545
Vic Davies.

742
00:54:58,546 --> 00:55:00,547
The only guy to ever win
three grand nationals.

743
00:55:00,548 --> 00:55:02,549
I'm still chasing
his lap record.

744
00:55:02,550 --> 00:55:08,005
Yeah, I heard of him.
Thanks for your time.

745
00:55:08,006 --> 00:55:10,641
Hey, what did you say
